      "text": "m_context        : VulkanContext*\nm_device         : Device*\nm_swapchain      : Swapchain*\nm_commandManager : CommandManager*\nm_syncObjects    : SyncObjects*\nm_postProcess    : PostProcessManager*\nm_cameraUniforms      : uptr<CameraUniforms>\nm_materialDescriptors : uptr<MaterialDescriptors>\nm_scenePipeline    : ScenePipeline\nm_deferredLighting : DeferredLightingPipeline\nm_sceneGeometry    : SceneGeometry   (road)\nm_dynamicGeometry  : SceneGeometry   (car)\nm_camera       : Camera*    (set by scene)\nm_currentFrame : uint32_t   (% 2 frames)\nm_texture/scene/modelManager*  (NOT owned)",
