      "text": "m_gbufferRenderPass + albedo/normal/material\n   images+views+FBs            [2 frames]\nm_lightingRenderPass + FBs + lightingSets\n   (set 1 of lighting = G-buffer samplers)\nm_hdrImages + m_hdrDepthImages  [2 frames]\nbloom extract/blurH/blurV imgs  (1/4 res)\nAO + AO-blur images   (1/2 res, dormant)\nm_compositeFBs : [per swapchain image]\nm_sampler (clamp-to-edge)\npipelines: bloomExtract, bloomBlur, composite\nPostProcessParams push: threshold,\n   bloom_intensity, exposure, texel_x/y",
