      "roundness": null,
      "text": "PASS CHAIN (per frame)\n\nG-buffer (opaque)\n  | albedo+normal+material+depth\n  v\nDeferred lighting -> HDR\n  | reads G-buffer via lightingSet\n  v\nBloom extract (1/4 res)\n  v\nBlur H  ->  Blur V\n  v\nComposite -> swapchain\n  ACES tonemap, bloom 0.3, exp 1.0\n\nplanned insert (rain seam):\nforward transparent pass\nbetween lighting and bloom",
      "originalText": "PASS CHAIN (per frame)\n\nG-buffer (opaque)\n  | albedo+normal+material+depth\n  v\nDeferred lighting -> HDR\n  | reads G-buffer via lightingSet\n  v\nBloom extract (1/4 res)\n  v\nBlur H  ->  Blur V\n  v\nComposite -> swapchain\n  ACES tonemap, bloom 0.3, exp 1.0\n\nplanned insert (rain seam):\nforward transparent pass\nbetween lighting and bloom",
