      "width": 453.59999999999997,
      "height": 87.5,
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "strokeColor": "#ffd43b",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "DESCRIPTOR-SET CONTRACT (fixed across the codebase)\n  set 0  =  CameraUniforms      camera + lights UBOs\n  set 1  =  MaterialDescriptors PBR textures (scene)\n            or G-buffer samplers (lighting pass)\n  set 2  =  reserved: future windshield-rain pass only",
      "originalText": "DESCRIPTOR-SET CONTRACT (fixed across the codebase)\n  set 0  =  CameraUniforms      camera + lights UBOs\n  set 1  =  MaterialDescriptors PBR textures (scene)\n            or G-buffer samplers (lighting pass)\n  set 2  =  reserved: future windshield-rain pass only",
