      "strokeColor": "#f1f3f5",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "CONSTANTS\n  MAX_FRAMES_IN_FLIGHT = 2   (utils/Types.h)\n  WORLD_SCALE = 1000         (1 m = 1000 WU)\n  HDR format R16G16B16A16_SFLOAT \u00b7 bloom 1/4 res \u00b7 AO 1/2 res",
