      "strokeColor": "#f1f3f5",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "OWNERSHIP RULES\n  Renderer owns all islands A-H objects except:\n  TextureManager / SceneManager / ModelManager -> owned by App,\n  registered via register_*()  \u00b7  Camera -> owned by Renderer, set by scene\n  rule: NO vkCmd*/vk* calls from scene code \u2014 route through these classes",
      "originalText": "OWNERSHIP RULES\n  Renderer owns all islands A-H objects except:\n  TextureManager / SceneManager / ModelManager -> owned by App,\n  registered via register_*()  \u00b7  Camera -> owned by Renderer, set by scene\n  rule: NO vkCmd*/vk* calls from scene code \u2014 route through these classes",
